# Component design patterns
- Maintain class ordering: layout → sizing → spacing → typography → visual → interatterns to Blade components
- Use `@apply` sparingly; prefer CSS-first config or dynamic utilities
- Prefix custom component classes with `c-ter/exit transitions (`starting:open:opacity-0`)
- Use `inert` variant for non-interactive elements

# Responsive & container queries
- Follow mobile-first design with standard breakpoints: `sm` (640px), `md` (768px), `lg` (1024px), `xl` (1280px), `2xl` (1536px)
- Wrap elements in `<div class="@container">` to enable container queries
- Combine `@min-*` and `@max-*` variants to define query ranges: `@min-md:@max-xl:hidden`
- Order variants in utilities: base → state → responsive → container → print

