## Core `container mx-auto`
- **Grid**: `grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6`
- **Flex**: `flex flex-col gap-4 justify-center`
- **Spacing**: `pt-0`, `pt-small`, `pb-normal` (via ACF settings)
- **Colors**: `bg-white`, `bg-light`, `bg-primary`, `text-secondary`
- **Typography**: `text-4xl`, `font-bold`, `leading-tight`, `prose`
- **Shadows & rings**: `shadow`, `inset-shadow-1`, `inset-ring-2`
- **Pointer & interaction**: `pointalid`, `user-invalid`
- **Gradients**: `bg-linear-to-r`, `bg-radial`, `bg-conic`, fiers
- **Transforms**: `transform-3d`, `rotate-x-45`, `translate-z-2`

